title: Celebrity Animal Ghost Stories
description:
Written by Alene Latimer
Starring Dan Hodapp, Langan Kingsley, Avery Monsen, Kelly Hudson, Jonathan Marballi, Lisa Kleinman

Directed by Laura Grey

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, May 5, 2014.

Edited by Ryan Hunter.
